      "suggestedVersionCode": "9",
      "description": "A simple LAN chat app built using Flutter. It allows users to chat with each other over a local network without the need for an internet connection. The app uses UDP sockets for communication and supports text messaging.",
      "issueTracker": "https://github.com/nihaltp/secret_chat/issues",
      "license": "MIT",
      "sourceCode": "https://github.com/nihaltp/secret_chat",
      "summary": "Peer-to-peer LAN chat app",
      "webSite": "https://nihaltp.github.io/secret_chat/",
      "added": 1775759883000,
      "packageName": "com.nihaltp.secret_chat",
      "lastUpdated": 1776194614000,
      "localized": {
        "en-US": {
          "description": "Secret Chat is a local area network (LAN) messaging application that allows you to chat with friends and colleagues without an internet connection. Perfect for conferences, offices, events, or any situation where you need secure, private communication within a local network.\n\nFeatures:\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 No Internet Required - Chat over your local WiFi or mobile hotspot\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Privacy Focused - Messages stay on your local network\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Multiple Security Options - Protect your rooms with passwords, PINs, or pattern locks\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Dark Theme - Easy on the eyes with built-in dark mode\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 App Lock - Biometric or screen lock protection for the entire app\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Hidden Rooms - Create private rooms that don't appear in the room list\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Message History - Messages persist while the app is running, cleared when closed\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Material Design 3 - Modern, clean interface\n\nHow to Use:\n1. Choose \"Host Network\" to create a room and share as the host\n2. Or choose \"Use Wi-Fi\" to browse and join existing rooms\n3. Optionally protect your room with a password, PIN, or pattern\n4. Start chatting - all communication stays within your local network\n\nSecurity:\n- All communication happens locally on your WiFi network\n- No data transmitted to external servers\n- Messages are not stored permanently\n- Supports biometric authentication\n- Pattern lock option for additional security\n\nPerfect for:\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Office communications and quick collaboration\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Conferences and events\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Classroom discussions\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 LAN parties and gaming events\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Emergency communication when internet is unavailable\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Privacy-conscious users who want local control",
          "icon": "icon_O_WgVXogi560N3_I3SgnduiPjuj0DtgbaKww1bp0n-A=.png",
          "name": "Secret Chat",
          "phoneScreenshots": [
            "1.png",
            "2.png",
            "3.png",
            "4.png"
          ],
          "summary": "LAN chat without internet - secure, private, instant messages",
          "whatsNew": "v1.2.1 - Padding Compatibility & Test Reliability\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Fixed message delivery between devices with different message padding settings (chunk size mismatch).\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Added cross-device tests for mismatched padding in both user and room chat.\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Improved failover test reliability (host readiness wait).\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 All tests and analyzer clean for release.\n"
        }
      }
    },
