      "added": 1776154885000,
      "packageName": "com.nihaltp.volume_lock",
      "lastUpdated": 1776232479000,
      "localized": {
        "en-US": {
          "description": "Volume Lock gives you fine-grained control over your Android audio behavior with two core features:\n\n- Volume Lock: when the screen turns off, current media, ring, notification, and alarm volumes are locked and automatically restored if changed.\n- App Volume Lock: saves and restores media volume for selected apps when you return to them.\n\nKey highlights:\n- Tracks and restores audio levels automatically\n- Lets you choose which apps participate in App Volume Lock\n- Keeps behavior consistent after reboot\n\nPermissions:\n- Do Not Disturb / Notification Policy access is needed to lock ring and notification volumes on Android 6+\n- Accessibility service is needed to detect foreground app changes for App Volume Lock\n\nBuilt with Flutter",
          "icon": "icon__l8Ngazf-gX_9fNTaj9ideVFpxVfdiPJ9GsR8lGmGks=.png",
          "name": "Volume Lock",
          "phoneScreenshots": [
            "1.png",
            "2.png",
            "3.png"
          ],
          "summary": "Lock device volume profiles and auto-restore per-app media volume.",
          "whatsNew": "Show all app icon/logo in app list. Fix bug for adaptive icon. Fallback to letter if icon missing. Many grunt.\n"
